    public class Option
extends MaterialWidget
    Option widget that encapsulated a <option> tag. This widget is to be used in conjunction with MaterialListBox: 

     
 <m:MaterialListBox >
     <m:html.Option text="One" value="1"/>
     <m:html.Option text="Two" value="2"/>
     <m:html.Option text="Three" value="3"/>
  </m:MaterialListBox>

    Author:
    gilberto-torrezan
    See Also:
    OptionElement
